About The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC Gender




Both men and women are well-represented.



About The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC Ethnicity




76% employees are White.



14% are Asian.



About The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC Skill




74% of applicants must know Data analysis.



65% also must know Product management.



Other top required skills include Business analysis, Program management, Project management, Leadership.



About The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC Degree




There are 18 times more applicants with a Bs than those with a Ms.



84% of applicants have a Bs.



8% have no degree.



6% have a Ms.



5% have a Cpa.



About The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC Base




A quarter of Base Salary for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are less than $89.2K.



Half of Base Salary for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are less than $98.5K.



The top quarter of Base Salary for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are more than $109K.



The top tenth of Base Salary for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are more than $119K.



About The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC Bonus




A quarter of Annual Bonus for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are less than $14.8K.



Half of Annual Bonus for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are less than $18.8K.



The top quarter of Annual Bonus for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are more than $23.9K.



The top tenth of Annual Bonus for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are more than $29.7K.



About The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC Equity




A quarter of Annual Equity for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are less than $6.72K.



Half of Annual Equity for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are less than $10.4K.



The top quarter of Annual Equity for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are more than $16.3K.



The top tenth of Annual Equity for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are more than $24.2K.



About The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC Total




A quarter of Total Annual Pay, including equity and annual bonus for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are less than $119K.



Half of Total Annual Pay, including equity and annual bonus for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are less than $131K.



The top quarter of Total Annual Pay, including equity and annual bonus for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are more than $144K.



The top tenth of Total Annual Pay, including equity and annual bonus for The Advisory Board Company Product Manager in Washington, DC are more than $158K.


